{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9348392/dababy-find-my-way-video|title=DaBaby's 'Find My Way' Video Tells a Tragic 'Bonnie & Clyde'-Inspired Tale: Watch|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|last=Gracie|first=Bianca|date=April 1, 2020|accessdate=April 1, 2020}}</ref> It shows DaBaby with B. Simone in a car, with flashbacks of the pair shooting people. They then check into in a hotel. Other patrons soon tell the hotel about them and the hotel staff knocks on DaBaby and Simone's hotel door and orders them to leave immediately saying they have two minutes to do so. DaBaby later talks from inside and uses obscene language. After, DaBaby and Simone do not talk, but Simone finds the gun and gives it to DaBaby. The hotel staff start shooting down the room to get in and DaBaby, who is hidden with Simone, begins returning fire.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2020/04/dababy-find-my-way-video|title=Watch DaBaby's Short Film for New Song \"Find My Way\"|work=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]|last=Espinoza|first=Joshua|date=April 1, 2020|accessdate=April 1, 2020}}</ref> The music video was filmed in the desert in California.\n\n=== Alternate ending ===\nDaBaby shared an alternate ending to the music video on April 8, 2020, with the caption \"Raise ya hand for the alternate ending ? \ud83d\ude4b\ud83c\udffe\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/dababys-find-my-way-music-video-has-an-alternate-ending-news.108108.html|title=DaBaby's \"Find My Way\" Music Video Has An Alternate Ending|last=|first=|date=|website=HotNewHipHop|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 12, 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Critical reception ==\nThe track received generally positive reviews. Bianca Gracie of ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' called the track \"melodic\".<ref name=\":0\" /> Mitch Findlay of ''[[HotNewHipHop]]'' was extremely positive about the song, calling it his \"most stylistically daring track in a minute\", saying it was \"certainly a promising direction for the rapper's upcoming third studio album\". He also said the track \"has all the making of a full-fledged hit\", and called the delivery \"passionate\" and \"confident\", and the production \"seductive yet dangerous\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/dababys-anticipated-find-my-way-has-arrived-new-song.1986741.html|title=DaBaby's Anticipated \"Find My Way\" Has Arrived|last=Findlay|first=Mitch|date=April 1, 2020|website=HotNewhipHop|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 12, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Commercial performance==\n\"Find My Way\" charted in the UK, Australia, New Zealand, and at number 22 on the US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]].\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=April 13, 2020|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}</ref>\n| 47\n|-\n{{single chart|Ireland4|25|date=20200410|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Hot Singles ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4845|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=April 13, 2020|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Sweden Heatseeker ([[Sverigetopplistan]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/215?dspy=2020&dspp=15|title=Veckolista Heatseeker, vecka 15|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n{{single chart|Switzerland|68|artist=DaBaby|song=Find My Way|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 13, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|UK|46|date=20200410|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}\n|-\